585
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:45,770
Fair enough.

586
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:52,480
You're still not coming out?

587
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,400
Take your time.

588
00:34:59,560 --> 00:35:00,760
Is there a nightgown?

589
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:21,320
Is your cover identity a dancer?

590
00:35:24,640 --> 00:35:25,880
Are our cover identities

591
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,210
supposed to be a couple?

592
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,600
I'm your superior.

593
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:34,000
I have the authority to give you orders.

594
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:34,580
Don't I?

595
00:35:35,040 --> 00:35:36,040
So remember this.

596
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:37,320
If you can talk nicely in the future,

597
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,880
then don't get physical. Understand?

598
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:40,240
But I don't know anything about you.

599
00:35:40,240 --> 00:35:41,200
How am I supposed to pretend to be your lover?

600
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:42,800
What do you mean you don't know?

601
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,640
You've seen my file,

602
00:35:43,640 --> 00:35:44,600
I've seen yours too.

603
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:46,040
That counts as knowing each other.

604
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:46,840
Files are just files.

605
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:47,720
People are people.

606
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,680
People are alive.

607
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,280
Then what do you want to know?

608
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:57,320
For example.

609
00:35:59,160 --> 00:36:00,000
Do you smoke?

610
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,180
Occasionally.

611
00:36:01,640 --> 00:36:02,440
Are you married?

612
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,160
No, I'm not.

613
00:36:04,560 --> 00:36:05,520
You don't look like someone who would be married.

614
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:06,840
What woman would want to marry you?

615
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,960
What about you? Are you married?

616
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:08,760
Of course not.

617
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:09,580
Be serious.

618
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:17,520
Didn't you want to know more?

619
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:20,800
Here's a book.

620
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:22,640
You can read English.

621
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,560
Read it as quickly as possible,

622
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:25,720
finish it,

623
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:28,720
and then tell me which passage interests you the most.

624
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:07,440
I'm still just a young girl.

625
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:10,600
I've never been in a relationship,

626
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:13,600
let alone slept with anyone.

627
00:37:14,080 --> 00:37:16,680
My training

628
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:19,240
never included this either.

629
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:20,920
I know I can trust you

630
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,480
and I must trust you.

631
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,920
But no matter what,

632
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:26,600
I cannot share a bed with you.

633
00:37:26,600 --> 00:37:27,840
Absolutely not.

634
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,480
I don't understand English

635
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:39,000
or anything at all.

636
00:37:44,080 --> 00:37:44,640
Donkey.

637
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:47,320
How cute.

638
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,000
Wumu.

639
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:01,000
I'm neither a stupid donkey

640
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:03,080
nor a foolish one.

641
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:07,320
I was born in the Year of the Ox,

642
00:38:07,680 --> 00:38:09,760
not the Year of the Donkey.

643
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:13,680
Let me put it this way,

644
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:16,640
you're casting pearls before swine,

645
00:38:16,640 --> 00:38:18,000
wasting your effort.

646
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:23,360
Please go to your own bed

647
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:25,080
and good night.

648
00:39:08,520 --> 00:39:09,880
Oh my God!

649
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,200
He took two dancers

650
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:15,280
from the Guotai Ballroom.

651
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:15,880
One of them

652
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,360
was the woman we saw today.

653
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,360
Then he took those two dancers

654
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:21,960
to his residence.

655
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:23,360
I believe

656
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:24,840
the envoy's woman went back

657
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:26,960
to get some change of clothes.

658
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:28,040
Finally,

659
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:29,320
the envoy took that woman

660
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:31,400
to the Metropole Hotel.

661
00:39:32,160 --> 00:39:33,960
Did they meet anyone special?

662
00:39:34,720 --> 00:39:35,980
Nothing was observed.

663
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:41,040
Someone close to the Emperor,

664
00:39:41,400 --> 00:39:42,560
coming to Shanghai,

665
00:39:42,560 --> 00:39:43,520
can't help indulging in pleasure

666
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:45,040
and debauchery.

667
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:46,320
Yes.

668
00:39:47,280 --> 00:39:50,760
What exactly is the envoy doing in Shanghai?

669
00:39:52,040 --> 00:39:53,440
The envoy came to Shanghai

670
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:56,100
but doesn't seem to have any official business.

671
00:39:57,640 --> 00:39:58,560
You may go now.

672
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:19,010
Connect me to the Garrison Headquarters.

673
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:23,440
This is Inoue Akira from the Inoue Mansion.

674
00:40:23,640 --> 00:40:26,840
I'm looking for Chief of Staff Tangchuan Yafu.

675
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:30,560
Alright, one moment...

676
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:32,280
Very good.

677
00:40:32,720 --> 00:40:34,440
Excellent.

678
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:35,320
Yes.

679
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:44,960
This is the first one.

680
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,220
Here's the second one.

681
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,280
I agree.

682
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:49,100
Major Channing Walker

683
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:52,680
graduated from Virginia Military Institute

684
00:40:53,160 --> 00:40:55,820
joined the Army Air Force Intelligence in 1939.

685
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:57,120
Isn't that right?

686
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:57,650
Yes, sir.

687
00:40:58,720 --> 00:40:59,240
Good.

688
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,400
Very good.

689
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:03,880
The Commander has a new assignment for you,

690
00:41:04,680 --> 00:41:05,600
Major.

691
00:41:05,800 --> 00:41:07,680
You are now officially appointed as

692
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:11,720
staff officer for Air Operations in the China Theater

693
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:14,040
and General Stilwell's air force assistant.

694
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:14,640
Yes, sir.

695
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,880
This is just your public identity.

696
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:17,840
Your real mission

697
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:18,720
Chief of Staff Harmon

698
00:41:18,720 --> 00:41:20,280
will brief you immediately.

699
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,340
Listen, Channing.

700
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,720
What I'm about to tell you

701
00:41:24,080 --> 00:41:25,840
is classified at the highest level.

702
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:28,040
Besides the people in this room

703
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:31,360
including the President of the United States,

704
00:41:31,360 --> 00:41:33,960
you are the eleventh person to know about this.

705
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:35,880
In two weeks,

706
00:41:35,880 --> 00:41:37,520
the Pacific Fleet with the Hornet

707
00:41:37,520 --> 00:41:39,080
and Enterprise as the main vessels

708
00:41:39,080 --> 00:41:42,120
will form a joint task force.

709
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:43,560
The fleet's mission

710
00:41:43,560 --> 00:41:44,560
is to transport one of our bomber squadrons

711
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,090
across the entire Pacific.

712
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:49,200
It will take eighteen days.

713
00:41:49,720 --> 00:41:51,640
The aircraft carriers will sail

714
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:54,000
to within 400 nautical miles of Japan.

715
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:55,680
Then,

716
00:41:56,640 --> 00:41:57,760
our bomber squadron

717
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,560
led by Lieutenant Colonel Jimmy Doolittle

718
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:01,600
their mission is to take off from the ships

719
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:03,320
fly to Tokyo.

720
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:05,880
Execute bombing missions.

721
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:07,920
Bomb Tokyo?

722
00:42:09,320 --> 00:42:10,040
Yes,

723
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,400
bomb Tokyo.

724
00:42:12,040 --> 00:42:13,680
To avenge the attack

725
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:15,280
on Pearl Harbor.

726
00:42:16,240 --> 00:42:17,700
Sir, how is that possible?

727
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:19,560
I've never heard of

728
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:20,200
Army bombers

729
00:42:20,200 --> 00:42:21,840
taking off from Navy ships.

730
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:24,800
This is indeed unprecedented and extremely risky.

731
00:42:24,800 --> 00:42:27,400
We want to send Japan a message

732
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:29,480
that their homeland is not safe.

733
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:32,260
Because the bombers cannot land on the deck,

734
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:35,420
after bombing Tokyo, the bombers must fly to China.

735
00:42:36,120 --> 00:42:39,160
They will land at a small airfield in China

736
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:40,920
near Quzhou.

737
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:43,840
So Channing, your mission is

738
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,920
to ensure their safe return.

739
00:42:46,520 --> 00:42:48,080
You need to arrive in China

740
00:42:48,080 --> 00:42:49,880
before Doolittle

741
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:52,400
to ensure they can land safely.

742
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:56,840
Safe landing is the only guarantee

743
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:59,320
to prevent this mission from being suicidal.

744
00:42:59,320 --> 00:43:00,040
The lives of the pilots

745
00:43:00,040 --> 00:43:01,800
participating in this raid hang in the balance.

746
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:03,880
Do you understand the importance of this mission?

747
00:43:03,880 --> 00:43:04,600
Yes, sir.

748
00:43:05,240 --> 00:43:06,280
I will do my utmost

749
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:07,360
to ensure Doolittle and his pilots

750
00:43:07,360 --> 00:43:08,560
return safely.

751
00:43:09,080 --> 00:43:09,720
Sir,

752
00:43:11,400 --> 00:43:14,160
the radio beacon call signs and codes

753
00:43:14,160 --> 00:43:15,800
are all in this Bible.

754
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:18,800
You will use these to make contact with Doolittle.

755
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:19,920
We've installed a self-destruct mechanism in the book

756
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:21,520
you only need to pull it once.

757
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:25,360
There's also an intelligence capsule in here, Channing.

758
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:27,160
I don't need to explain further.

759
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:28,240
No need, sir.

760
00:43:30,880 --> 00:43:31,960
Remember,

761
00:43:32,200 --> 00:43:33,520
in the China Theater, only two people know about this

762
00:43:33,520 --> 00:43:35,160
and can help you.

763
00:43:35,920 --> 00:43:37,320
The Supreme Commander of the China Theater,

764
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:38,240
Chiang Kai-shek,

765
00:43:38,240 --> 00:43:39,520
and General Stilwell, Chief of Staff of the China Theater.

766
00:43:39,520 --> 00:43:40,520
Understood, sir.

767
00:43:40,640 --> 00:43:41,770
I'll remember that.

768
00:43:42,120 --> 00:43:44,040
You should be aware

769
00:43:44,040 --> 00:43:46,280
that you're not our first Believer.

770
00:43:46,840 --> 00:43:48,920
Your predecessor was shot down

771
00:43:48,920 --> 00:43:50,980
while entering China through Burma.

772
00:43:52,240 --> 00:43:53,520
He's still missing.

773
00:43:54,400 --> 00:43:54,960
Yes, sir.

774
00:43:55,680 --> 00:43:56,480
In two hours,

775
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:57,840
a plane will take you to India first,

776
00:43:57,840 --> 00:43:59,900
then from India to General Stilwell.

777
00:44:00,200 --> 00:44:02,240
Remember your soldier's oath.

778
00:44:03,880 --> 00:44:04,680
Good luck.

779
00:44:05,040 --> 00:44:05,640
Yes, sir.

780
00:44:05,720 --> 00:44:06,850
I won't let you down.

781
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:09,880
God bless you.

782
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,320
Thank you, sir.

783
00:44:14,280 --> 00:44:17,160
March 20, 1942.

784
00:44:17,560 --> 00:44:18,960
The U.S. Army Department

785
00:44:18,960 --> 00:44:21,920
sent the second Believer, Cheney,

786
00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:26,120
to replace Witt who was trapped on Sanzao Island.
